  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13056222/shutterstock_108771737_web.png" alt="Ballroom Dancing in Lake Bled" rel="858,410" /></div>
<div> </div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>With the growing popularity of programmes like Strictly Come Dancing, we're sure that our 'Slovenia &amp; Dance' holiday will be a memorable experience with your hosts, Philip Wylie, Christine Parsons and Team presenting Modern Ballroom, Latin American and some Popular Sequences at the 4* Hotel Lovec in Bled. The hotel's Panorama Hall boasts the most stunning views across <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13056223/slo_dancing_katarina_venturini_02_webjpg.png" alt="Slovenia Ballroom Dancing Katarina Venturini" rel="858,410" /></div>
<div> </div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>The holiday price of <strong>£TBC per person</strong> XX XXXX 2019 weeks includes: return flights from Stansted &amp; transfers / 7 nights half board / Full dance programme / 'Learn &amp; Improve' workshops / Free trip to city of <a data-udi="umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721}" title="Ljubljana">Ljubljana</a> / Services of Inghams Resort Rep.</p>
<p><strong>Other UK airports available</strong>. Supplement for twin with Balcony £TBC per persons per night; Single room £TBC per person per night.</p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
